# Gmail API Client Code Review Report

## Executive Summary

I've completed a comprehensive security and quality review of the Gmail API client implementation in `/workspaces/gmail-automation/packages/email-processor/src/gmail/gmail-client.ts` and its test suite. The implementation demonstrates **strong foundational security practices** and **good code quality**, but there are **critical security gaps** and **production readiness concerns** that must be addressed before deployment.

**Overall Assessment:** ⚠️ **HIGH PRIORITY FIXES REQUIRED** before production deployment

**Test Coverage:** 92.59% line coverage, 85.71% branch coverage (excellent)

